  > |
  > B
  > |
  > A
  > EOF

create master bookmark

  $ hg bookmark master_bookmark -r tip

blobimport them into Mononoke storage and start Mononoke
  $ cd ..
  $ blobimport repo-hg/.hg repo

start mononoke
  $ start_and_wait_for_mononoke_server
